Package: aiddata
Title: Access AidData API from R Console
Description: Functions to access and download AidData through the AidData 3.0
    API. Allows the user to download a list of aid projects for a given country
    and year(s), as well as information on the geolocation of aid projects (if
    available).
Version: 0.1
Imports:
    httr,
    dplyr,
    data.table
Suggests:
    knitr,
    raster,
    countrycode
Authors@R: person("Felix", "Haass", email = "haass.felix@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
